message: The I-20 corridor and the I-85 corridor are hot spots for human trafficking. This includes Chambers County, Auburn, Opelika, Valley, Lanett and West Point along I-85.  People are trafficked for cheap or free labor, sex, and to sell drugs.  #I85 #notforsaleb https://buff.ly/2GhpwwD
